column5: One more!
And finally!
More great pictures Matt, looks like that big ole girl has lost a few teeth over the years.

LOL , yes she does seem to be  a little shy in the tooth dept. I was wondering how much of that was due to the hookset and fight. She was hooked in her left side corner of the mouth or right side as you look at the pic, the sheer weight and pull was incredible as she dragged that bait back and forth over the jaw as she battled.
Yeah, a fight like that with a big bait in her mouth could sure do some damage to her teeth I'd imagine.
OK Matt... you and your gang are on 'em... we get it. lol.  Nicely done again bud.  Congrats to Luc on a huge Ottawa R. ski.

Wow, what a fish. Luc and I have hooked up fishing together through FB twice this year. The first time I lost a giant, today Luc more than made up for it with this giant.  52.125" long and an incredible head and girth.  It hit a bucktail while working a shallow weed edge.  Man am I going to replay it coming into view in my head for a few days lol
Very nice thick fish. Way to go.
Wow !!!! Awesome fish man !!!! Congrats a fish of a lifetime !!!!
The sens suck, j/k. Wicked fish, super thick!!!
Wowzers, that is a beast.  Well done!!!!
Atta boy Luc, very nice fish indeed !!
I've caught Perch and Sheephead bigger than that Way to go man, that is a fish of a life time  You'll be dreaming about that fish in your dreams
Great fish, congrats!
Awesome catch.  Congrats.  I'll bet she was a load of fun to bring in.   Thanks or putting up her pic.
very nice ski for sure congrats thanks for taking the time to post it Cheers
Great Catch! good looking fish!
Incredible fish! Congrats!
That's great Terry, been awhile since you posted one of those
Haha awesome. I don't even know if Luc frequents here but he's going to now. Great job Terry.
Now that's a serious beast!!!! Looks at the size of it's head!!!! Imagine how big it would get by November!!!! Nice fish man.
Man!  That's a thick fish!
That .125 must have been tough to see on the tape  :)  Nice fish man!
Not for a carpenter!!
yup, that's a giant alright!
Beauty !! my 5 th time out ..my times coming
wow! what else can you say!  a life day for sure
Awesome fish....
Gotta like underwater photography!  Another shot of the big girl
